WEBVTT

00:00:02.790 --> 00:00:04.000
Hello.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.635
I'm a toy developer.

00:00:06.845 --> 00:00:10.899
With a dream of creating new toys
that have never been seen before,

00:00:10.899 --> 00:00:13.506
I began working at a toy company
nine years ago.

00:00:14.026 --> 00:00:16.062
When I first started working there,

00:00:16.062 --> 00:00:20.020
I proposed many new ideas
to my boss every day.

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:22.838
However, my boss always asked

00:00:22.838 --> 00:00:25.442
if I had the data to prove it would sell,

00:00:25.442 --> 00:00:28.875
and asked me to think of product
development after analyzing market data.

00:00:28.875 --> 00:00:30.289
Data, data, data.